Version 0.9.5 (2011-10-27)
* added __constructor method to adhere to CakePHP 2.0 Migration policy
* removed $config parameter from initialize method to adhere to CakePHP 2.0 Migration policy
* added $config options 'max_file_size' and 'allowed_image_file_types'
* modified is_image method taking new config option into consideration
* added file size check in upload_FS method
* added format_bytes function to format file size

